am faakats fatatabin to,
Ana Tsoiny Mumua tan nainy pisiin te ruak me ana Tsunaun Jisas te atsuiny ya, fiisen men fuas tana nguen Ya ana Ya te rurei vavis ya, fifiisen men siinaiv reits tana tou tabin me Tsunia fiisen men siinaiv.
Nyo komainy tsue of marom senviir tsue te kat anyo tan nainy te pon ma naa fi nyo tana gum fan iny Masedonia, nyi ma naus osing tsom vaare na ngats fan iny Efeses, sana nyi ma kaa tsom em na aya, nyi te faan iny tsuen parits tana tee vainy ma faonot ari, ri te faatsuts vaare na vainy tan gum iny vainy fafaaman tsuam tan fafaatsuts gamgam.
Sikia ma Adam to te faamainy gam ten Satan, a moun te faamainy gam ten Satan, ana ya ruak iny muiny kat kat aveto mito.
Sana nyi ma fataanis osing a fo siisio babainy tana fo tsuvurara muan, a sikia ta man nane Gov tsunia. A sikia, faatsuts a tsivom tan faparits a aavem, tan kat tavaron ten Gov,
